# aladdin_wakeword.tflite — Placeholder

## Download Instructions
Place your real TFLite wake-word model here:
  app/src/main/assets/aladdin_wakeword.tflite

Options:
  1. Porcupine wake-word: https://github.com/Picovoice/porcupine
  2. Custom TFLite model trained with transfer learning

The WakeWordDetector will load this via AssetManager.
